I '''Alan Cooper''', metung yang talapanustus ning [[interaction design]], tatalan yang deseniung cumpania at susulat yangaklat (libru) nung makananung gawan ing software [[makarap talagamit (user interface)]] mas [[Usability|gamitan]] ya.

I Cooper neng misan mayayaus yang "tatang ning [[Visual Basic]]", agiang keraklan ning meobra keng  Visual Basic gewa ne ning [[Microsoft]] a lupung da reng pangkilub a manalkus. I Cooper iya ing memuntukan o menimunu gulut ning VB 1.0 ampong menimuna keng pamangamit keng IDE para agamit ya ing [[GUI]] kapamilatan ning ausan dang makabalut a aus kareng [[system routines]] keng API (lawen ya ing [[Adapter pattern]]).

Ing mumuna nang programang Cooper meyaus lang "Tripod" at kaibat "Ruby"<ref>http://www.cooper.com/alan/father_of_vb.html</ref>. They were intended as more of an end-user tool, but development at Microsoft led to Visual Basic becoming a tool for programmers instead.

